<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="ko">

<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8" />
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0" />
    <title>EMA522_02_SU_0004_s</title>

    <!-- 공통 js-->
    <script src="../../common_contents/common/js/app.js"></script>

    <!-- 공통 css-->
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="./../../common_contents/common/css/app.css" />

    <!-- 개별 -->
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="./../../common_contents/css/ema522_02_su.css" />
</head>

<body>
    <div id="app_wrap" class="ema522_02_su_0004">
        <section class="title type2">
            <h2 data-head="2" lang="y" class="fraction_box_title">
                <div class="fraction_txt_wrap">
                    <div class="fraction_txt" lang="y">
                        <div class="operation_box ml_0">
                            <div class="fraction_box">
                                <span>3</span>
                                <span>5</span>
                            </div>
                            <span>&times;2</span>
                        </div>
                        를 어떻게 계산하는지 알아봅시다.
                    </div>
                </div>
            </h2>
        </section>

        <section class="contents paging_layout">
            <article class="page page_1">

                <h3 lang="y">
                    <div class="fraction_txt_wrap">
                        <div class="fraction_txt" lang="y">
                            그림을 보고
                            <div class="operation_box">
                                <div class="fraction_box">
                                    <span>3</span>
                                    <span>5</span>
                                </div>
                                <span>&times;</span>2
                            </div>
                            를 계산하는 방법을 알아보세요.
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </h3>
                <img src="../../common_contents/img/EMA522_02_SU/0004_img01.png" alt="자치회 활동 이미지" />

                <div class="question_box justify_center mt_50">
                    <div class="mixed_fraction f32b gap_0">
                        <span class="fraction_box">
                            <span>3</span>
                            <span>5</span>
                        </span>
                        <span>&times;2</span>
                        <span>=</span>
                        <span class="fraction_box">
                            <span>3</span>
                            <span>5</span>
                        </span>
                        <span>+</span>
                        <span class="fraction_box">
                            <span>3</span>
                            <span>5</span>
                        </span>
                        <span>=</span>
                        <span class="fraction_box">
                            <span>3+3</span>
                            <span>5</span>
                        </span>
                        <span>=</span>
                        <!-- <div class="group_box"> -->
                        <span class="fraction_box">
                            <span class="flex justify_center">
                                <span>3&times;</span>
                                <span class="input_wrap">
                                    <math-field data-answer-single="2" placeholder=" "></math-field>
                                </span>
                            </span>
                            <span>5</span>
                        </span>
                        <!-- </div> -->
                        <span>=</span>

                        <!-- <div class="group_box"> -->
                        <span class="fraction_box">
                            <span class="input_wrap">
                                <math-field data-answer-single="6" placeholder=" "></math-field>
                            </span>
                            <span>5</span>
                        </span>
                        <span>=</span>
                        <span class="input_wrap">
                            <math-field data-answer-single="1" placeholder=" "></math-field>
                        </span>
                        <span class="fraction_box">
                            <span class="input_wrap">
                                <math-field data-answer-single="1" placeholder=" "></math-field>
                            </span>
                            <span>
                                <span>5</span>
                            </span>
                        </span>
                        <!-- </div> -->
                    </div>
                </div>
            </article>
            <article class="page page_2">
                <h3 lang="y">(진분수)×(자연수)를 계산하는 방법을 이야기해 보세요.</h3>

                <div class="input_area m_auto">
                    <div class="input_wrap">
                        <math-field class="textarea" id="inputElement01" type="text"></math-field>
                        <div class="example_box">
                            <p lang="y">분모는 그대로 쓰고 분자에 자연수를 곱하여 계산합니다.</p>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </article>
            <article class="page page_3">
                <div class="summarize_wrap">
                    <div class="summarize">
                        <label lang="y">정리해 볼까요</label>
                        <div class="flex dir_col gap_20">
                            <span lang="y">(진분수)×(자연수)는 분수의 분모는 그대로 쓰고</span>
                            <span>
                                <button class="reveal_btn mr_8">분자</button>
                                <span class="small-gap" lang="y">에 자연수를 곱하여 계산합니다.</span>
                            </span>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </article>

            <div class="btn_area">
                <button class="btnType key">입력타입토글</button>
                <button class="btnReset">리셋</button>
                <button class="btnCheck">확인</button>
                <button class="btnSubmit">확인</button>
            </div>
        </section>
    </div>
</body>

</html>